comment:
If even IGN gave this game a 4/10 than it sure is a sign that this franchise is doomed.
The only pros for this game would still be the gameplay.
As for cons: -the story is kinda like the one from MW2(2009) and a bit from MW3(2011);
-even if we have open-combat missions,you can finish the campaign in just 3 hours(even less than MW1 and MW2);
-the game isn't optimization (you need between 178/215 gb free space)
